DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.CurveId, T1.SeqSegment, T1.Seq, T5.Quote AS Quote FROM ORE.dbo.CurveConfigurationQuotes T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.MdatMarketDataDefinitions T5 ON T1.Quote = T5.Quote ORDER BY 1 ASC, 2 ASC, 3 ASC

field.name: *Quote
field.lookup: SELECT Quote,Quote Lookup FROM ORE.dbo.MdatMarketDataDefinitions ORDER BY Quote
